      "content": "that's a good start for the tone. can you expand on that? like, maybe include some of his specific observations about the \"inherent differences\" between the British and the locals that justify why they can't just govern themselves? he should probably mention why their culture or way of life makes them \"unfit\" for modern governance compared to the British.",
